Regulation (EEC) No 1764/86 is amended as follows:
1. Article 8 is replaced by the following:
2. Article 9 is replaced by the following:
(a) common salt (sodium chloride);
(b) natural spices, aromatic herbs and their extracts, and natural aromas.
(a) not exceed 15 % by weight of the dry weight content for tomato concentrate having a dry weight content exceeding 20 %;
(b) not exceed 3 % by weight of the net weight for other tomato concentrates and for tomato juice;
(c) be between 2 % and 5 % by weight for kunserva.
